' commit: d5549c6 (deep-review 批 C 收口)
' description: archive_plan tool 改变的 5 个 entity 并行 state machine (plan / worktree / git branch / cwdReleaseMarker / callerSession + teammate)
' last_updated: 2026-05-28
@startuml archive-plan-state-machine

title archive_plan — 5 entity 并行 state 联动 (Step 1-7 + runBatonCleanup phase 1+2)

' ─── entity 1: plan frontmatter (file content) ───
state "Plan Frontmatter\n(<plan-file-path>)" as PlanState {
  state "status: in_progress" as InProgress
  state "status: completed\n+ final_commit\n+ completed_at" as Completed
  state "status: abandoned\n(手工 §Step 4 §中止)" as Abandoned

  [*] --> InProgress : enter_worktree\n(plan 创建时写 frontmatter)
  InProgress --> Completed : archive_plan Step 3\n(writeFrontmatter)
  InProgress --> Abandoned : 手工 §Step 4 §中止\n(不入 git 归档)
  Completed --> [*]
  Abandoned --> [*]
}

' ─── entity 2: worktree (filesystem + git) ───
state "Worktree dir\n(.claude/worktrees/<plan-id>/)" as WorktreeState {
  state "exists\n(创建后 in-use)" as WorktreeExists
  state "removed\n(git worktree remove)" as WorktreeRemoved

  [*] --> WorktreeExists : enter_worktree Step 2
  WorktreeExists --> WorktreeRemoved : archive_plan Step 7b\n(precondition: clean + Step 2 ff-merge OK)
  WorktreeRemoved --> [*]
}

' ─── entity 3: git branch (worktree-<plan-id>) ───
state "Git branch\nworktree-<plan-id>" as BranchState {
  state "exists\n(enter_worktree -b)" as BranchExists
  state "merged to base_branch\n(--ff-only)" as BranchMerged
  state "deleted\n(git branch -D)" as BranchDeleted

  [*] --> BranchExists : enter_worktree Step 1
  BranchExists --> BranchMerged : archive_plan Step 2\n(merge --ff-only worktree-<id>)
  BranchMerged --> BranchDeleted : archive_plan Step 7c\n(branch -D worktree-<id>)
  BranchDeleted --> [*]
}

' ─── entity 4: sessionRepo.cwdReleaseMarker (DB column) ───
state "callerSession.cwdReleaseMarker\n(DB column)" as MarkerState {
  state "null\n(plan/worktree 未关联)" as MarkerNull
  state "set = <worktreePath>\n(enter_worktree marker)" as MarkerSet

  [*] --> MarkerNull
  MarkerNull --> MarkerSet : enter_worktree(plan-driven)\nsessionRepo.setCwdReleaseMarker
  MarkerSet --> MarkerNull : archive_plan Step 7a\nclearCwdReleaseMarker
  note right of MarkerSet
    F10 修法 (REVIEW_59 批 A):
    Step 7a 提前到 commit 后,
    Step 7b/c 失败时 marker 已清
    caller 跑别 plan 不撞 stale marker reject
  end note
}

' ─── entity 5: caller + teammate sessions (DB + in-memory) ───
state "Caller + Teammate sessions" as SessionState {
  state "caller: active\n+ teammate: active/dormant" as SessionsActive
  state "teammate: closed\n+ caller: active" as TeammateClosed
  state "teammate: closed\n+ caller: archived" as AllArchived

  [*] --> SessionsActive
  SessionsActive --> TeammateClosed : runBatonCleanup phase 1\nshutdownTeammatesOnBaton
  note right of TeammateClosed
    plan hand-off-session-adopt-teammates-20260520 P3:
    archive_plan 永远跑 phase 1 (不再支持 opt-out)
    plan 收口 = team 整片收口
    teammate.cwdReleaseMarker 不动 (per-session)
  end note
  TeammateClosed --> AllArchived : runBatonCleanup phase 2\narchiveSourceSessionWithEmit(callerSid)
  note right of AllArchived
    phase 2 失败 → archived='failed' warn-only
    不阻塞 ok return
    eventBus.emit 'session-status-changed' 让 UI sync
  end note
  AllArchived --> [*]
}

' ─── 跨 entity 时序串联 (5 entity Step 1-7 + phase 1+2 同步切换) ───

note as N1
  archive_plan tool **原子时序**(任一失败立即 abort 无部分回滚):

  ① Plan: InProgress → 走 Step 3 writeFrontmatter → Completed
  ② Worktree: WorktreeExists → 走 Step 7b git worktree remove → WorktreeRemoved
  ③ Branch: BranchExists → Step 2 ff-merge → BranchMerged → Step 7c branch -D → BranchDeleted
  ④ Marker: MarkerSet → Step 7a clearCwdReleaseMarker → MarkerNull (F10 提前)
  ⑤ Sessions: SessionsActive → phase 1 → TeammateClosed → phase 2 → AllArchived

  失败兜底:
  - Step 1-6 任一失败 → 4 entity 全停在「未变」状态(plan/worktree/branch/marker 未变)+ 5 entity SessionsActive 不动
  - Step 7a 失败 (marker clear) → 仅 archive 错(marker stale 不会污染后续 plan)
  - Step 7b/c 失败 → marker 已清(F10 修法)+ worktree/branch 状态由 caller 手工 cleanup
  - phase 1 单 teammate close fail → 仅该 teammate warn,其他继续 close
  - phase 2 archive caller fail → archived='failed' warn-only,5 entity 中 caller 仍 active

  与 K2 hand_off_session baton 时序对比:
  - hand_off: spawn 新 session → reassignTaskOwner → phase 1+2 (与 archive_plan 同款)
  - archive_plan: 不 spawn 新 session,Step 1-7 + phase 1+2 = plan/worktree/team 整片收口
end note

@enduml
